~⊞⁻¹-preserves-is-all-del (d₀Del ∷ Γ₀Del) (d₁Del ∷ Γ₁Del) (d~ ∷ Γ~) = ~d⊞⁻¹-preserves-is-del d₀Del d₁Del d~ ∷ ~⊞⁻¹-preserves-is-all-del Γ₀Del Γ₁Del Γ~

